Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}原来在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:13.36,D5-Answer,,0,0,0,,梨花！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}你们等着 蛆虫们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}只要我吃下特效药
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}好痒 好痒 好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}应该是这个
