Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}别捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}我只是想治好我这蛆虫病
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}可恶的蛆虫 蛆蛆蛆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}越来越多了
